Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要杀了奈落?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.69,0:01:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.43,0:01:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从跟那个家伙有所瓜葛之后\N就没有什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.43,0:01:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老是出现一些碍手碍脚的麻烦事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:01:58.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连帮母亲大人\N冲淡身上毒素的人血
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.03,0:02:00.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也反而变得越来越难收集了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.24,0:02:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最不能原谅的是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.17,0:02:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然让我阿毘公主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.78,0:02:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卷入了他们半妖之间\N无聊的争斗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.85,0:02:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.38,0:02:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你不如试着\N去攻打那个城堡看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.38,0:02:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.79,0:02:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一个非常可疑的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.46,0:02:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕跟奈落有着很深的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲大人  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚好跟那个圣大人\N差不多时候出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.23,0:02:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.24,0:02:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖鸟烧起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣大人终于回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.13,0:03:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救…救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.80,0:03:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是布下结界的那个家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:08.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.92,0:03:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得…得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的鸟全都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.12,0:03:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.99,0:03:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从遇上奈落之后\N就一直遇到碍事的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么看来那个圣大人\N好像是奈落的眼中钉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:48.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落释放出手下的妖怪\N布满了整个天空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到处寻找\N那个圣大人的藏身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经派出鸟儿\N去调查这样的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:03:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果发现只有一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些妖怪完全没有接近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.96,0:04:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是一个人类的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.06,0:04:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落的妖怪\N就像没有看见城堡一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.40,0:04:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从上空飞了过去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.70,0:04:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是因为这个地方\N跟奈落有着关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.47,0:04:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才没有必要去搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.21,0:04:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你试着去袭击那个城堡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.91,0:04:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看奈落到底在那个地方\N隐藏了什么秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.15,0:04:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第152话\N保护并且夺取
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.66,0:04:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您看看少爷睡得很甜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:41.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上也从来不哭闹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是一个乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛那天晚上可怕的事件\N从来没有发生过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在我生下这个孩子\N的那天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时在产房里帮忙的所有人\N全部都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.12,0:05:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有某个人出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在却想不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.26,0:05:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后那个晚上的记忆\N就越来越淡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀  不能去那里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以进来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在是非常的抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子\N是刚来我们这不久的下人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有习惯这个地方的环境
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.79,0:05:43.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.29,0:05:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫他抬起头\N让我看看他的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.79,0:05:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.56,0:05:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抬起头来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.36,0:05:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.14,0:05:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是不是在哪里见过面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.44,0:06:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个孩子\N怎么可能有机会见过夫人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.58,0:06:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是我多心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人看起来\N好像是一位很温柔的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.28,0:06:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且夫人最近刚生了嗣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.85,0:06:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.49,0:06:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:54.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和神无\N一起留在那个城堡里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在城堡里面生活\N保护好那个婴儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.37,0:07:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀  要多吃一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把这些柴搬走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.18,0:07:46.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个城堡好平静
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像也曾经像这样\N跟很多人生活在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.92,0:07:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我已经想不起来\N那是什么时候的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.37,0:08:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  一群吸人血的鸟群
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您知道这件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.11,0:08:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近好像都在传这件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们当然也有听说过\N这个传闻啰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么这附近有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.68,0:08:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从来都没有看过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.62,0:08:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且这里就在城堡的山脚下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.66,0:08:32.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪们肯定是不能靠近这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也不是我们要找的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.57,0:08:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.20,0:08:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又没有妖鸟巢穴的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.64,0:08:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我们今天只好先在这里\N借宿一晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说只好借宿一晚是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.18,0:08:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.28,0:08:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我们一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:09:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也好想玩呀…\N但还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:04.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.09,0:09:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不够教训
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白童子这个小鬼没有心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:16.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不管被怎么四分五裂\N都不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.05,0:09:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙的心脏到底在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.12,0:09:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐  你在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少啰唆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.72,0:09:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总得让我有想的自由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.63,0:09:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个叫什么\N鸟之使者阿毘公主吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.74,0:09:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐  跟在她们后面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要监视着就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.97,0:09:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准你多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:57.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多管闲事是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.35,0:09:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.22,0:10:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奈落的毒虫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来监视我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走着瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女妖怪\N已经变成奈落的敌人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀  琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.53,0:10:51.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听到你在呻吟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.04,0:10:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是做恶梦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么样的梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.51,0:11:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好点了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.56,0:11:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来要做个好梦喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.80,0:11:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙一开始打呼\N其他人就没办法好好睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都好亲切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.59,0:11:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么  不感谢我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.76,0:11:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我奈落\N把你弟弟的命捡回来的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀  你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要保护奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让他忘记了全部的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于你的事\N还有琥珀所有的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:13.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗得好舒服喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.62,0:12:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  你也去洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是阿毘公主的妖鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝城堡的方向去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀\N你连父母的样子都不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.04,0:12:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争中失去父母的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.25,0:12:48.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.82,0:12:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  还好你来到这城堡\N和大家在一块
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里工作的每一个人\N就像是一家人感情很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.91,0:13:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是妖鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.95,0:13:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险啊  快躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.99,0:13:29.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥…琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.43,0:13:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不能出去外面  知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.20,0:13:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.44,0:13:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀  去保护那个婴儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.12,0:14:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有这个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.99,0:14:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城堡里所有的人\N都会保护我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.23,0:14:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是牺牲自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些妖鸟出动了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们正在袭击城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.64,0:14:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有四魂之玉碎片的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀身上的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.91,0:14:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀在城堡里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个气息一定是他没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.51,0:14:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀\N你又受到了奈落的命令吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:28.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次你又打算做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.03,0:14:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀  去保护那个婴儿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护嗣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让它们靠近屋内
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.14,0:14:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道这些妖鸟\N是因为知道婴儿在这里而来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这个地方干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是个下人的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点找个地方躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.45,0:15:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.69,0:15:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们保护了我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.80,0:15:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到了城堡之后\N就直接去找琥珀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖鸟让我来对付
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去啊  珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.31,0:15:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.08,0:15:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉碎片的气息\N在那个方向
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.58,0:15:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云母
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.55,0:15:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.09,0:15:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  又是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿毘公主\N你还没受够教训啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:54.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.13,0:15:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是奈落的敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.57,0:15:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你为什么要保护这个城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.31,0:16:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个城堡…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成这里跟奈落有什么关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我要来证明的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然现在出来抵抗的\N就只有人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.02,0:16:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.75,0:16:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是已经跟奈落联手了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.82,0:16:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.26,0:16:20.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那家伙一厢情愿而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说你跟奈落已经闹翻啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.86,0:16:25.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就不要再插手多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落那个家伙由我们来打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.60,0:16:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我先来解决你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.97,0:16:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我滚回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来跟奈落扯上关系\N唯一的好处
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.41,0:16:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概就是这把三叉戟的结界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.05,0:16:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瘴气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.45,0:16:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这个作用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.46,0:16:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少得意了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.07,0:17:03.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让阿毘公主跟犬夜叉两个人\N互相厮杀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.57,0:17:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎不是奈落计划的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个城堡里到底有什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.25,0:17:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖鸟烧起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.06,0:17:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,着火了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人  您快点到外头去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.38,0:17:44.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再待在这里的话会被烧死的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是那个叫琥珀的孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是外头有妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:56.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么样\N我都必须保护这个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:17:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他是很重要的嗣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:17:59.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会用自己的生命来保护他的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  往这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.38,0:18:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.67,0:18:46.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这孩子救了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.57,0:18:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:51.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀  我要谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.55,0:18:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.72,0:18:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须让夫人他们\N到安全一点的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:18:59.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀  你就待在夫人的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.05,0:19:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.59,0:19:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖鸟又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.20,0:19:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你帮了我大忙  琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往那边了  大家快点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.87,0:19:17.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我问你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.91,0:19:20.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在哪里学会这些本领的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是看着别人模仿的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来好像是驱魔师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托掩护一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.65,0:19:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驱魔师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.52,0:19:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前好像也像这样战斗过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.90,0:19:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟伙伴们一起同心协力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.91,0:19:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:55.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:19.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下受到妖鸟的攻击了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.43,0:20:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城堡…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.14,0:20:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被攻陷了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.81,0:20:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.08,0:20:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧的  夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.65,0:20:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀  把婴儿抢过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把周遭的人通通杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.86,0:20:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.47,0:20:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:20:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一定…一定会得救的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀  你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.33,0:21:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好  琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.06,0:21:24.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.07,0:21:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.57,0:21:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀掉
